@startuml Screen Navigation

skinparam BackgroundColor #ffffff
skinparam ArrowColor #555555
skinparam ArrowFontColor #333333
skinparam StateBorderColor #555555
skinparam StateBackgroundColor #f5f5f5
skinparam StateFontColor #111111
skinparam NoteBackgroundColor #ddeeff
skinparam NoteBorderColor #5588bb
skinparam NoteFontColor #111111

title Sub-Pro Workstation — Screen Navigation Map

[*] --> FirstRun : first launch\n(no password set)
FirstRun --> Workflow : password created

[*] --> Workflow : subsequent launches\n(password exists)

state Workflow {
}

state History {
}

state Settings {
}

state Unlock {
}

state FirstRun {
}

Workflow --> History   : NavBar > History
Workflow --> Settings  : NavBar > Settings [password]
Workflow --> Unlock    : NavBar > Unlock [password]

History  --> Workflow  : NavBar > Home
History  --> Settings  : NavBar > Settings [password]
History  --> Unlock    : NavBar > Unlock [password]

Settings --> Workflow  : NavBar > Home
Settings --> History   : NavBar > History
Settings --> Unlock    : NavBar > Unlock [password]

Unlock   --> Workflow  : NavBar > Home
Unlock   --> History   : NavBar > History
Unlock   --> Settings  : NavBar > Settings [password]

note right of Workflow
  During an active scan, Settings and Unlock
  are disabled (session_active = True).
end note

note right of Settings
  Settings has three tabs: Device & Firmware; Parts;
  and Change Password.
end note

@enduml
